00:40:27.991 --> 00:40:29.720
I'm like, there's
so much stuff I used

00:40:29.720 --> 00:40:31.040
to do for the wrong reason.

00:40:31.040 --> 00:40:34.350
I just didn't understand
who I was as a person.

00:40:34.350 --> 00:40:36.724
And in starting to just
kind of let stuff go,

00:40:36.724 --> 00:40:39.140
that was the first time I
really started to figure it out.

00:40:39.140 --> 00:40:40.910
And I'm like, the
answers were so simple.

00:40:40.910 --> 00:40:42.289
I'm like, I'm a writer.

00:40:42.289 --> 00:40:42.830
I'm a reader.

00:40:42.830 --> 00:40:44.220
So I like books.

00:40:44.220 --> 00:40:44.959
I'm a writer.

