you almost are hitting a pause

00:42:06.933 --> 00:42:08.910
button and asking
yourself a few questions

00:42:08.910 --> 00:42:10.420
before you're doing it.

00:42:10.420 --> 00:42:12.709
So instead of just automatically
making the purchase,

00:42:12.709 --> 00:42:15.250
